                        <interp inst="t18740921-name-45" type="surname" value="RYAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18740921-name-45" type="given" value="PATRICK"></interp>PATRICK RYAN</persName>
                  </hi>* (<hi rend="italic">City Policeman</hi> 748). I was called to Mr. Krapper's and took the prisoner—I found an apron folded up and concealed inside his waistcoat—Mr. Krapper gave me these two bad shillings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. WEBSTER</hi>. These three shillings are bad.</p>
